                     <div class="article.text"> 
                     <h3 class="article-title">{{post.data.title}}DIOR ADDICT STELLAR HALO SHINE</h3>
                     <h4 class="article-price">{{post.data.price}}>$38.00</h4>
                     <h4 class="article-info">By {{post.data.info}} "This balm glides on with incredible sensoriality and instantly melts on contact with the lips. The luscious lip care formula creates a fine film infused with aloe vera for 24h hydration*** and long-lasting comfort, wrapped in the soft, addictive scent of vanilla with a hint of musk.</h4>
